# Git Commit Conventions

Follow these rules when making Git commits:

## Reference

- [AngularJS Git Commit Message Conventions](https://github.com/angular/angular.js/blob/master/CONTRIBUTING.md#commit)
- See `CONTRIBUTING.md` (English) or `CONTRIBUTING-CHT.md` (繁體中文)

## Format

```
<type>(<scope>): <subject>

<body>

<footer>
```

## Rules

1. **Language**: Commit messages may be written in **English** or **Traditional Chinese**
2. **subject**: Imperative mood, present tense, no leading capital, no trailing period
3. **Line length**: Max 100 characters per line

## Type Reference

| Type | English | 繁體中文 |
|------|---------|---------|
| feat | New feature | 新功能 |
| fix | Bug fix | 錯誤修復 |
| docs | Documentation | 文件 |
| style | Code style | 格式 |
| refactor | Refactoring | 重構 |
| test | Tests | 測試 |
| chore | Build/maintenance | 建置/維護 |

## Examples

```
feat(pdf): add PDF margin cropping
feat(pdf): 新增 PDF 留白裁切功能
chore: initialize project structure
fix(cli): fix output filename error
```
